Can you leave a link to this in a comment: https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/xcb2z8hs.aspx

That explains how to do it for Windows, but it is somewhat a moot point because it only works when debugging (i.e. Windows ps equivalent does not show this info) and no one debugs adb on Windows because the build process does not generate PDB debugging files (because gcc doesn't produce it, unlike Visual Studio).

