If you want to see other implementations of setting a thread name, see ART SetThreadName: http://androidxref.com/5.1.1_r6/xref/art/runtime/utils.cc#987 , and libutils/Threads.cpp: androidSetThreadName. I think the former handles all the Linux vs. MacOS, plus the 16 char max which is a real headache.

